data.description: What a find! Welcomed home with beautiful mahogany floors throughout. Custom kitchen adjoins the breakfast room that walks out to the patio. Private Master suite with luxury bath & walk in closets. Main floor is completed with 2 additional bedrooms, a full bath, & main floor laundry. My favorite feature is the all-seasons room surrounded by windows that walks out to the patio overlooking the backyard; the perfect place to hangout or relax. Lower level offers the finished basement with bar area situated in theater room with projector and projector screen, a family/rec room, full bath, & two storage areas. Other amenities include open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, over 2,400sqft total living space, Smart alarm system, Smart garage door opener & garage heater, & updated landscaping. Ready for immediate occupancy! RELOCATION LISTING. AGENTS SEE RELO packets & INSTRUCTIONS in supplements. Seller negotiates verbally and RELO requires 3-5 Business days.
